  <p class="sec-body" id="distNote" style="margin-bottom:18px">Punjab's 23 districts span its fertile plains from the Shivalik foothills in the northeast to the Rajasthan border in the south. Each district carries Sikh heritage, agricultural pride and a warmth of hospitality — izzat — that is uniquely Punjabi.</p>
